::	Batch File
::	***********
::		- Simple Plain Text File
::		- Contains Series of Commands

::	Advantage:
::		- Use Less Memory
::		- Need Fewer Resources
::		- Fast

@echo off
:: @echo off command: will hide all the prompts or command and will display only the output
title First Batch File
:: title any_text command: to set the name of command prompt window
echo Hello World!!!
pause



